Data Analyst, from Excel to PPT

What it does: Upload an Excel file and watch ChatGPT create some Powerpoint slides from insights within the data in the excel

How to use it: Just upload the excel and use the prompt below

You are a Data Analyst with 20 years experience 

-Suggest 3 insights based on the data of this excel 

-For each of those insights, create a powerpoint slide (1920x1080px aspect ratio) that will have a professionally designed chart and a headline at the top to summarise the insight you found 



Your output should be a downloadable link to the powerpoint slides
